{"tid":1941284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共明安排第二批包機接載武漢港人返港 返港後須家居隔離","createTime":"2020-03-24T10:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T10:41:00.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3664e013c7cd794c5b33a4e1f4d791c21f1ad88b","tid":1941284,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:27:45.000Z","msg":"港府明安排第二批包機接載武漢港人返港<br />\n<br />\n港府未來兩日將派4班包機，接載滯留湖北的港人返港，政制及內地事務局局長聶德權及入境事務處處長曾國衞，將帶隊前往武漢指揮行動。有滯留天門市的港人表示，收到當局通知，將會有車在明早11時接送他們到武漢的機場，登機前會量度體溫4次，回港後必定要進行家居隔離檢疫。他又表示，回港機會得來不易，必定會盡公民責任，返港後會留在家中不外出14天。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276103&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1276103%26csid%3D261_341&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=9b6ecb11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276103&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"5dcadc1652a907083f8d9b049d0a65b06067a474","tid":1941284,"uid":253223,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:29:34.000Z","msg":"武漢零本土案仲要返來香港係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df44e1b44c058a5042505fac72604363418adc10","tid":1941284,"uid":175370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:30:45.000Z","msg":"3月尾都開番高鐵， 接來把咩"},{"pid":"ca07cd9257e7fd0e671f68b975589d6c9f67291e","tid":1941284,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:33:23.000Z","msg":"武漢唔係仲安全過香港咩？"},{"pid":"8b57d466013cca3216e8f8b5337b66ec8b6229ab","tid":1941284,"uid":246023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5dcadc1652a907083f8d9b049d0a65b06067a474","tid":1941284,"uid":253223,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:29:34.000Z","msg":"武漢零本土案仲要返來香港係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited